CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778351320
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to agree exit
OL,4,Cplan after election losses
OL,6,FMr Burgon warned against a "stitch up"
OL,7,Fof the type that prevented Andy
OL,8,FBurnham from standing in the Gorton
OL,9,Fand Denton by-election.
OL,11,FThe Greater Manchester mayor is widely
OL,12,Fviewed as a potential challenger to
OL,13,FSir Keir if he can find a way to win a
OL,14,Fby-election to return to Westminster.
OL,26,@nD@\OUnD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778351320
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to agree exit
OL,4,Cplan after election losses
OL,6,FAndrea Egan, general secretary of the
OL,7,FUnison union, warned "Labour faces
OL,8,Fpolitical oblivion because it's simply
OL,9,Fnot delivering for the majority of
OL,10,Fpeople" and "there'll clearly be a
OL,11,Fchange of Labour leader sooner or
OL,12,Flater".
OL,14,FBut an apparently co-ordinated
OL,15,Fcampaign was mounted to shore up
OL,16,Fsupport for Sir Keir, with ministers
OL,17,Fand Labour grandees warning against
OL,18,Fthe disruption of a leadership contest.
OL,26,@oD@VOUrD@GO]rD@MOUtD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
