PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778351320
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to agree exit
OL,4,Cplan after election losses
OL,6,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,7,Fsaid the results were "brutal" but
OL,8,F"the last thing we need is to descend
OL,9,Finto a vanity leadership contest",
OL,10,Fwhile others warned against "navel-
OL,11,Fgazing" and "just blaming the boss".
OL,13,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting, who
OL,14,Fhas continued to attract speculation
OL,15,Fabout his ambitions despite publicly
OL,16,Fdenying plans for a leadership tilt,
OL,17,Fsaid the Prime Minister will "have my
OL,18,Fsupport" in setting out how the
OL,19,Fgovernment will move forward on Monday.
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@^O]pD@AOUqD@aO]rD@]OUsD@GO]sD@
OL,26,AMOUsD@cO]yD@^OUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778351320
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to agree exit
OL,4,Cplan after election losses
OL,6,FBut facing questions from reporters on
OL,7,FFriday night as he attended the count
OL,8,Ffor Redbridge Council, where the party
OL,9,Fhopes to hold on to its majority, he
OL,10,Fdeclined to say whether he believed
OL,11,FSir Keir was the right person to lead
OL,12,FLabour into the next general election.
OL,14,F"I'll continue putting my shoulder to
OL,15,Fthe wheel as the Health and Social
OL,16,FCare Secretary, who's getting the NHS
OL,17,Fback on its feet and making sure it's
OL,18,Ffit for the future," he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
