OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to agree exit
OL,4,Cplan after election losses
OL,6,FKey developments after 127 of 136
OL,7,FEnglish councils had declared full
OL,8,Fresults are:
OL,10,F` Labour had lost control of 31
OL,11,Fcouncils and suffered a net loss of
OL,12,F1,022 seats.
OL,14,F` Reform gained control of 12 councils
OL,15,Fand added 1,244 seats.
OL,17,F` The Conservatives suffered a net
OL,18,Floss of eight councils and 417
OL,19,Fcouncillors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778351320
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to agree exit
OL,4,Cplan after election losses
OL,6,F` The Liberal Democrats won three
OL,7,Fcouncils and gained a net 146 seats.
OL,9,F` The Green Party gained control of
OL,10,Ffour councils and put on 297
OL,11,Fcouncillors.
OL,13,F` In Scotland, after 80 results out of
OL,14,F81 constituencies and regions, the SNP
OL,15,Fhad 57 seats, Labour 17, Reform 15,
OL,16,Fthe Scottish Greens 13, the
OL,17,FConservatives 11 and the Liberal
OL,18,FDemocrats nine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
