OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to agree exit
OL,4,Cplan after election losses
OL,6,F` In Wales, Plaid Cymru have 43 seats
OL,7,Fin the Senedd, with Reform on 34,
OL,8,FLabour on nine, the Conservatives on
OL,9,Fseven, the Greens on two and the
OL,10,FLiberal Democrats on one.
